import React from "react"
import '../assets/css/Busquedas.css'

import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
import InfiniteGrid from '../src/grid';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'



class objeto_pregunta extends React.Component{

  render(){
    return(
    <Card border="success" style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
      <Card.Header>Header</Card.Header>
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Success Card Title</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk
          of the card's content.
        </Card.Text>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
    )
  }
}


class Busquedas extends React.Component{
  constructor(props) {
    super(props);
    this.referencia = React.createRef();
    this.preguntas = []
  }

  realizarBusqueda(){
    console.log('holi bebe')
  }

  render(){
    return(
      <Container id='component_busqueda' fluid='true'>
        <Row top="xs">
          <Col md={4}>
            <Card>
              <Card.Header id='card_header'>Busqueda de preguntas en la BBDD</Card.Header>
                <Card.Body id='busqueda_card_body'>
                  <Container id='busqueda_card_body_container' fluid='true'>
                    <Row top="xs">
                      <Col md={6}>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Asignatura" id='form_element'/>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Asignatura" id='form_element'/>
                      </Col>
                      <Col>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Asignatura" id='form_element'/>
                      </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Button onClick={this.realizarBusqueda} id='standard_button' >Buscar</Button>
                  </Container>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
          </Col>
          <Col>
            <Card id='search_result_card'>
              <Card.Header id='card_header' > Resultados </Card.Header>
              <Card.Body id='card_body_result_container'>
                <Container fluid='true'>
                  <Row top="xs">
                    <Col id='search_result_container'>

                    </Col>
                  </Row>
                </Container>
              </Card.Body>
            </Card>
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    )
  }
}

export default Busquedas
